snippet.title: GSMC Social Media News Podcast Episode 20: Jan Brady, Amber Heard, & Uber
snippet.description:
GSMC Social Media News Podcast Episode 20: Jan Brady, Amber Heard, & Uber's Driverless Cars (8-22-16)

    In this episode Pauline and Mariano discuss former Brady Bunch star, Eve Plumb and the selling of her home she bought at 11 years old. The two continue on to talk about Amber Heard and what she has done with the money she received from her divorce with Johnny Depp. To wrap up the episode, Pauliano give their opinions on the pros and cons of the new driverless Uber cars debuting this fall.

    Follow the GSMC Social Media News Podcast at http://www.gsmcpodcast.com/social-media-podcast.html
